Soylo A Cuck Boy Story - MGTOW


MGTOW Mystery Link:

Hi Everyone Sandman Here,

This video is brought to you by a donation from Deo Proximo and here's what he has to say: "Hello Sandman, I think there needs to be another video about Star Wars considering what's been going on since The Last Jedi came out. There are too many problems with Star Wars to talk about in one video, but the channels called SC Reviews, Geeks and Gamers and WorldClassBSers talk about these problems in a lot of detail. What's happened with Star Wars since Disney took over and injected identity politics into it shows that Feminists don't create anything original, but they hijack something that men built and run it into the ground. Kathleen Kennedy wearing The Force is Female t shirt says a lot about how Feminists hijack things and feminize it. The good thing about this is that it does Red Pill so many people. With the Hans Solo movie being a flop it shows that Star Wars is no longer the guaranteed success it used to be and there's a possibility that Episode 9 could be a flop. If that happens then Disney will be left holding a $4 billion lemon. Feminism is a race to the bottom and right now Disney is taking first place. Time magazine gives Person of the Year to organizations so I think we should nominate Disney for Mangina of the Year. Disney could compete with Justin Trudeau, the superboss of Manginas. Disney has put a minority of Feminists ahead of the majority of the Star Wars fans who watch the movies and buy the toys and ruined a cultural phenomenon." Well Deo Proximo thanks for the donation and topic. I'll put this one out sooner than usual but just so you know I have a fifty day backlog right now. Just so that everyone knows this isn't a review because I haven't seen the film nor do I want to and I would consider myself a fan until I watched The Last Jedi and decided I wasn't going to watch another Star Wars film until Disney gets it's act together. I believe they will once they start losing money. I will watch episode nine if the reviews are positive from the audience and not the critics. Disney is a business and if they can keep Marvel relatively SJW free than I'm sure they will get to cleaning up Star Wars as well. So why is this happening to Star Wars now? Everyone seems to think that it all comes down to the management decissions of Kathleen Kennedy. That she's all about pushing for more female roles in the films and trying to push a feminist agenda. There is talk that she's going to step aside in the fall. It seems that even putting in Dinerius Targarian in wasn't enough to fill the seats. But who really wants Seth McFarlanes' sloppy seconds anyways? There's even a picture of Alden Ehrenreich in this video where doesn't look very happy at the premiere. He probably knew that this film would ruin his movie career and probably wished he never took it. Of course feminists are trying to inject identity politics into what men watch and enjoy. First of all they want the money from the roles that male actors are typically cast in. Second they want to change male behavior and attitudes in our society and as more men walk away into video games, comics, movies and other solitary pursuits women are trying to catch up and influence male behavior on our turf.
